    {
      "id": "crisis.4101",
      "name": {
        "en": "Galactic Crisis Declared",
        "zh": "宣告星系危机"
      },
      "desc": {
        "en": "The Imperial Senate has passed a resolution declaring the §H[new_crisis.GetName]§! a threat to all sapient life and a crisis of galactic proportions. As a consequence, the [new_crisis.GetName] finds itself in a state of war with the entirety of the Imperium.\\n\\nIn a public announcement transmitted from [gal_emperor.Capital.GetName], the [gal_emperor.GetRulerTitle] called upon all members of the Imperium to mobilize their fleets and launch a concerted attack on [new_crisis.GetSpeciesName] territory: \"The galaxy and the Imperium will not know peace until the [new_crisis.GetSpeciesName] menace has been dealt with once and for all.\"",
        "zh": "帝国参议院通过了一项议案，宣布§H[new_crisis.GetName]§!是一切智慧生命体的威胁、是一场全星系范围的危机。从结果来说，[new_crisis.GetName]在今日同整个星海帝国开战了。\n\n在一场自[gal_emperor.Capital.GetName]对外播放的公开演讲中，[gal_emperor.GetRulerTitle]呼吁帝国的全体成员国对舰队进行总动员，并针对[new_crisis.GetSpeciesName]的领域发动联合攻击：“直到[new_crisis.GetSpeciesName]威胁被彻底地、一劳永逸地扫除干净，否则星系不会见证真正的和平。”"
      },
      "type": "country_event",
      "options": [
        {
          "en": "Can their rampage be stopped?",
          "zh": "我们能够阻止他们的蹂躏吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "crisis.4105",
      "name": {
        "en": "Community Declares Us \"Galactic Crisis\"",
        "zh": "共同体指定我方为“星系危机”"
      },
      "desc": {
        "en": "{",
        "zh": "{"
      },
      "type": "country_event",
      "options": [
        {
          "en": "This will be glorious.",
          "zh": "荣光无垠！"
        },
        {
          "en": "This is madness!",
          "zh": "疯了，全他妈疯了！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
