    {
      "id": "crisis.4110",
      "name": {
        "en": "Crisis Repealed",
        "zh": "天灾指定已废止"
      },
      "desc": {
        "en": "The resolution designating the §H[former_crisis.GetName]§! as a \"galactic crisis\" has been repealed by the Galactic Senate. As a result, all ongoing military operations being conducted by Community members against the [former_crisis.GetSpeciesNamePlural] are to cease at once. For now, peace has returned to this corner of the galaxy.",
        "zh": "指定§H[former_crisis.GetName]§!为“星系危机”的议案如今已被星海参议院废止。作为结果，所有由星海共同体成员国针对[former_crisis.GetSpeciesNamePlural]展开的军事行动都被立马叫停。现在，和平已经降临了星系的这一隅。"
      },
      "type": "country_event",
      "options": [
        {
          "en": "Will it last?",
          "zh": "和平又能持续多久呢？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "crisis.4111",
      "name": {
        "en": "Crisis Repealed",
        "zh": "天灾指定已废止"
      },
      "desc": {
        "en": "{",
        "zh": "{"
      },
      "type": "country_event",
      "options": [
        {
          "en": "So they came to their senses.",
          "zh": "理智终于占领了他们大脑的高地了。"
        },
        {
          "en": "They fear us!",
          "zh": "怕了吧，怕了吧！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "crisis.4112",
      "name": {
        "en": "Crisis Repealed",
        "zh": "天灾指定已废止"
      },
      "desc": {
        "en": "The resolution designating the §H[former_crisis.GetName]§! as a \"galactic crisis\" has been repealed by the Imperial Senate. Consequently, the [gal_emperor.GetRulerTitle] has ordered an immediate cessation of all ongoing Imperial military operations targeting the [former_crisis.GetSpeciesNamePlural]. For now, peace has returned to this corner of the galaxy.",
        "zh": "指定§H[former_crisis.GetName]§!为“星系危机”的议案如今已被帝国参议院废止。作为结果，[gal_emperor.GetRulerTitle]正式下令停止一切针对[former_crisis.GetSpeciesNamePlural]的帝国军事行动。现在，和平已经降临了星系的这一隅。"
      },
      "type": "country_event",
      "options": [
        {
          "en": "Will it last?",
          "zh": "和平又能持续多久呢？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "crisis.4113",
      "name": {
        "en": "Crisis Repealed",
        "zh": "天灾指定已废止"
      },
      "desc": {
        "en": "The Galactic Imperium has repealed the resolution declaring us a \"crisis\" and all Imperial forces have been ordered to stand down. Their [gal_emperor.GetRulerTitle] has commanded the cessation of all hostilities against us... for now.",
        "zh": "星海帝国已经废止了宣布我们为“星系危机”的议案，所有帝国军队均接到指令原地待命。[gal_emperor.GetRulerTitle]下令中止一切针对我们的敌对行动……暂时如此。"
      },
      "type": "country_event",
      "options": [
        {
          "en": "So they came to their senses.",
          "zh": "理智终于占领了他们大脑的高地了。"
        },
        {
          "en": "They fear us!",
          "zh": "怕了吧，怕了吧！"
        }
      ]
